metadata.name: Chrysalis I
metadata.description:
A sense of non-belonging // 

The subject is caught in a state of oblivion. He tries to come to terms with his sense of self, while trapped in a transient space: a newfound period of evolution. 

How does one complete the transformation into a destined higher being? This metamorphosis is both reassuring and dauntingâ€”through it, he is forced to reckon with the relationship between his past, present, and future ego.
